<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Nouvelle demande de commande — ProTIC Editions</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            background: #f0f4f8;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #1f2937;
        }

        .wrapper  { background: #f0f4f8; padding: 32px 16px; }
        .card     {
            max-width: 620px; margin: 0 auto;
            background: #fff; border-radius: 14px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(13,31,78,.12);
        }

        /* ── Header bleu ── */
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #06122e 0%, #0d1f4e 55%, #1a3a8f 100%);
            padding: 36px 40px 28px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header__logo  { font-size: 26px; font-weight: 800; color: #fff; letter-spacing: .02em; }
        .header__sub   { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,.50); letter-spacing: .12em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 2px; }
        .header__badge {
            display: inline-block; margin-top: 16px;
            background: rgba(253,217,9,.15); border: 1px solid rgba(253,217,9,.35);
            color: #fdd909; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: .06em; text-transform: uppercase;
            padding: 5px 14px; border-radius: 20px;
        }
        .header__title {
            font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff;
            margin-top: 12px; line-height: 1.35;
        }

        /* ── Bande or ── */
        .gold-bar {
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #0d1f4e, #1a3a8f 40%, #fdd909 70%, #0d1f4e);
        }

        /* ── Alerte ── */
        .alert {
            background: #fef9c3; border-left: 4px solid #fdd909;
            padding: 14px 24px; font-size: 13px; color: #78350f; line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* ── Corps ── */
        .body { padding: 32px 40px; }

        /* Section title */
        .section-title {
            font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; color: #1a3a8f;
            text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .10em;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
            padding-bottom: 8px; margin: 28px 0 16px;
        }
        .section-title:first-child { margin-top: 0; }

        /* Table infos */
        .info-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
        .info-row td {
            padding: 9px 0; font-size: 14px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
            vertical-align: top;
        }
        .info-row:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
        .info-label { width: 38%; color: #6b7280; font-weight: 600; padding-right: 12px; }
        .info-value { color: #1f2937; }
        .info-value a { color: #1a3a8f; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; }

        /* Message box */
        .msg-box {
            background: #f5f0e8;
            border-left: 4px solid #1a3a8f;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            font-size: 14px; color: #374151;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        /* Book card */
        .book-card {
            display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: flex-start;
            background: #f5f0e8; border: 1px solid #e5d9c5;
            border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px; margin-top: 8px;
        }
        .book-card__cover {
            width: 56px; height: 76px; border-radius: 5px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d1f4e, #1a3a8f);
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            font-size: 22px; flex-shrink: 0; overflow: hidden;
        }
        .book-card__cover img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
        .book-card__title  { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #0d1f4e; }
        .book-card__author { font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 4px; }
        .book-card__cat    {
            display: inline-block; margin-top: 8px;
            background: #0d1f4e; color: #fdd909;
            font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .05em;
            padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px; text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        /* Statut badge */
        .badge-pending {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #fef9c3; color: #78350f;
            border: 1px solid #fde68a;
            font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
            padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 20px;
        }

        /* CTA bouton */
        .cta-wrap { text-align: center; margin-top: 32px; }
        .cta-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a3a8f, #2d5be3);
            color: #fff !important; text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; padding: 13px 30px;
            border-radius: 8px; letter-spacing: .02em;
        }

        /* Meta bar */
        .meta {
            background: #f8fafc; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            padding: 12px 40px; font-size: 11px; color: #9ca3af;
            display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            background: #0d1f4e; padding: 22px 40px; text-align: center;
        }
        .footer p { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,.40); line-height: 1.75; }
        .footer strong { color: rgba(255,255,255,.65); }
        .footer a { color: #fdd909; text-decoration: none; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="wrapper">
<div class="card">

    {# ── Header ── #}
    <div class="header">
        <div class="header__logo">ProTIC</div>
        <div class="header__sub">Editions &amp; Services</div>
        <div class="header__badge">📩 Nouvelle demande de commande</div>
        <div class="header__title">{{ contact.subject }}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="gold-bar"></div>

    {# ── Alerte ── #}
    <div class="alert">
        <strong>⚡ Action requise :</strong>
        Un lecteur souhaite acquérir un exemplaire de votre livre.
        Contactez-le dans les <strong>48 heures</strong>
        à l'adresse <strong>{{ contact.email }}</strong>.
    </div>

    {# ── Corps ── #}
    <div class="body">

        {# Livre concerné #}
        {% if book %}
        <div class="section-title">📚 Livre concerné</div>
        <div class="book-card">
            <div class="book-card__cover">
                {% if book.coverImage %}
                    <img src="{{ absolute_url(asset('uploads/cover_image_book/' ~ book.coverImage)) }}"
                         alt="{{ book.title }}">
                {% else %}
                    📖
                {% endif %}
            </div>
            <div>
                <div class="book-card__title">{{ book.title }}</div>
                {% if book.subtitle %}
                    <div class="book-card__author" style="font-style:italic">{{ book.subtitle }}</div>
                {% endif %}
                <div class="book-card__author">
                    ✍️
                    {% if authorFullName %}
                        {{ authorFullName }}
                    {% else %}
                        Auteur inconnu
                    {% endif %}
                </div>
                {% if book.category.name %}
                    <span class="book-card__cat">{{ book.category.name }}</span>
                {% endif %}
            </div>
        </div>
        {% endif %}

        {# Informations du demandeur #}
        <div class="section-title">👤 Informations du demandeur</div>
        <table class="info-table">
            <tr class="info-row">
                <td class="info-label">Nom complet</td>
                <td class="info-value"><strong>{{ contact.fullName }}</strong></td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="info-row">
                <td class="info-label">Email</td>
                <td class="info-value">
                    <a href="mailto:{{ contact.email }}">{{ contact.email }}</a>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="info-row">
                <td class="info-label">Téléphone</td>
                <td class="info-value">
                    {% if contact.phone is defined and contact.phone is not empty %}
                        {% set value = contact.phone  %}
                        <a href="tel:+{{ value.countryCode }}{{ value.nationalNumber }}" style="color:#1a3a8f;">
                           +{{ value.countryCode }} {{ value.nationalNumber }}
                        </a>
                    {% else %}
                        <span style="color:#9ca3af;font-style:italic">Non renseigné</span>
                    {% endif %}
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="info-row">
                <td class="info-label">Pays</td>
                <td class="info-value">
                    {% if contact.country %}
                        {{ contact.country|u.truncate(2)|country_name('fr')|upper }}
                    {% else %}
                        <span style="color:#9ca3af;font-style:italic">Non renseigné</span>
                    {% endif %}
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="info-row">
                <td class="info-label">Date d'envoi</td>
                <td class="info-value">
                    {{ contact.sentAt|date('d/m/Y à H:i', 'Africa/Porto-Novo') }}
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="info-row">
                <td class="info-label">Statut</td>
                <td class="info-value">
                    <span class="badge-pending">En attente</span>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        {# Message du demandeur #}
        <div class="section-title">💬 Message</div>
        <div class="msg-box">{{ contact.message|nl2br }}</div>

        {# CTA #}
        <div class="cta-wrap">
            <a href="mailto:{{ contact.email }}?subject=Re: {{ contact.subject|url_encode }}"
               class="cta-btn">
                Répondre à {{ contact.fullName }} →
            </a>
        </div>

    </div>

    {# ── Meta ── #}
    <div class="meta">
        <span><strong>Réf :</strong> #{{ contact.id }}</span>
        <span><strong>Reçu le :</strong> {{ contact.sentAt|date('d/m/Y H:i:s', 'Africa/Porto-Novo') }}</span>
    </div>

    {# ── Footer ── #}
    <div class="footer">
        <p>
            Cet email est généré automatiquement par <strong>ProTIC Editions &amp; Services</strong>.<br>
            Répondez directement à <a href="mailto:{{ contact.email }}">{{ contact.email }}</a>
            pour contacter le demandeur.<br><br>
            © {{ "now"|date("Y") }} <strong>ProTIC Editions &amp; Services</strong> —
            Campus d'Abomey-Calavi, K61-62, Bénin<br>
            Développé par <strong>INTERNATIONALES WEB APPS &amp; SERVICES(+229 01 67251886)</strong>
        </p>
    </div>

</div>
</div>

</body>
</html>